          <item id="uid27">Write a balanced equation to show how each of the following ionic compounds dissociate in water.
<list id="id336252" display="block" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item id="uid28">sodium sulphate (<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi mathvariant="normal">Na</m:mi><m:msub><m:mrow/><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub><m:mi mathvariant="normal">SO</m:mi><m:msub><m:mrow/><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msub></m:math>)
